# .dockerignore — trim the build context for deploy/docker/Dockerfile.* (PR 4.8).
#
# The release build needs Cargo.toml, Cargo.lock, crates/, tests/ (workspace members),
# migrations/ (sqlx::migrate! embeds migrations/control at compile time) and .sqlx/ (the offline
# query cache). Everything below is excluded so the context stays small and layer-cacheable — most
# importantly target/, which is many gigabytes of build artifacts.
target/
**/target/
.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.claude/
docs/
*.md
